---
/* ============================================================================
   Homepage
   ============================================================================
   Three-act homepage architecture (replaces the previous eight-section frame).
   Section order is the IA, not decoration:

     Act 1  Hero        — full-bleed Cincinnati photograph + studio wordmark +
                          positioning + two CTAs. The one decisive image that
                          sets register for the rest of the page.
     Act 2  Selected    — three featured case studies, asymmetric (one large
            Work          + two medium). Real client names, real metrics, real
                          links into /work/{slug} for the long form.
     Act 3  Process     — single dark navy band that combines the four-step
            Band          process and the inquiry CTA. Closes the page with
                          one strong block instead of three stacked sections.

   The Footer is rendered by BaseLayout, immediately under Act 3, so the page
   ends on one continuous navy block from Act 3 through Footer.

   Services, PhotoStrip, and Testimonials are no longer separate homepage
   sections; each was re-homed where it belongs:
     - Services        → /services and /about already carry the offering copy.
     - PhotoStrip      → /photography is the dedicated photography surface;
                         a single Nathan-shot photograph carries the brand on
                         the homepage via the Hero image itself.
     - Testimonials    → embedded inside individual case study pages where
                         the quote has earned context.

   Architecture decision documented in PRODUCT.md and the rewrite-homepage
   shape brief (run via /impeccable shape) — refresh that doc if the three-act
   frame ever needs to shift.
   ============================================================================ */

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ProofBand from '../components/ProofBand.astro';
import SelectedWork from '../components/SelectedWork.astro';
import ProcessBand from '../components/ProcessBand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Nixon Creative Studio | Strategy-led design and photography">
  <Hero />
  <ProofBand />
  <SelectedWork />
  <ProcessBand />
</BaseLayout>
